    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/2f8427b03127fe48c21cd43d5dc464fd.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/2f8427b03127fe48c21cd43d5dc464fd.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/2f8427b03127fe48c21cd43d5dc464fd.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若是拥有神力，你会作出怎样的选择？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神命 - 神祗模拟器，你要建造定居点，并与其他神明争夺影响力。信徒越多，你所掌握的力量就越强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/249b5d12dabf073154657844034f17fb.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/249b5d12dabf073154657844034f17fb.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/249b5d12dabf073154657844034f17fb.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个上帝模拟游戏，你不仅要建立定居点，还要与其他神明争夺影响力。在《神命》中，你的追随者越多，你所拥有的权力就越大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理管理你的法力值来操纵你的定居点、信徒和现实本身的结构。随着你积聚更多的力量，更不俗的事迹等待你去解锁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6f56f4924195a5f3999b7fdc68d41737.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6f56f4924195a5f3999b7fdc68d41737.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6f56f4924195a5f3999b7fdc68d41737.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在白天，好好利用你对凡人的影响。你是要祝福和鼓励他们做善事，还是用可怕的幻象让他们心生恐惧？请三思而行，镇民有他们自己的意志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在晚上，你可以尽情操纵定居点。指示凡人为你建造寺庙供人膜拜，建造农场和木材厂以便他们繁荣，甚至毁掉其他村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6a2a2e7df974ca85dfe9c427bfba55ff.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6a2a2e7df974ca85dfe9c427bfba55ff.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/6a2a2e7df974ca85dfe9c427bfba55ff.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许你选择成为一个暴君，统治一个放荡而血腥的王国。培养一支军队，献祭你的人民来召唤可怕的恶魔。当然，你说了算。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者，你寄希望于欢乐、庆典与传播爱，但却毫不介意通过传播恐惧来削弱你的敌人——也许更直接一点，用雷击来削弱他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许你选择成为一个暴君，统治一个放荡而血腥的王国。培养一支军队，献祭你的人民来召唤可怕的恶魔。当然，你说了算。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者，你寄希望于欢乐、庆典与传播爱，但却毫不介意通过传播恐惧来削弱你的敌人——也许更直接一点，用雷击来削弱他们。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>塑造一个鲜活的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你影响力的增长，你的世界将随之成型，变得更加广阔。每个神明都以不同的方式表现着他们的王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的王国是庄稼与光明之国，还是扭曲丛林中的黑暗王国？你将与暴力之神、欺骗之神、生育之神和快乐之神对峙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/d4a6dafa2a880a6ebe66048811285482.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/d4a6dafa2a880a6ebe66048811285482.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/d4a6dafa2a880a6ebe66048811285482.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亲历专属传奇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成命运女神们亲自设下的重重挑战，书写属于你的传奇——从一名年轻的神明，成长为声名远扬、受人敬仰的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/7e845bf13e93c8f8a99fc15621553a2d.poster.avif?t=1759080655\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/7e845bf13e93c8f8a99fc15621553a2d.webm?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330360/extras/7e845bf13e93c8f8a99fc15621553a2d.mp4?t=1759080655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
